HEADWORD: Burrel fly
<hw>Bur"rel fly`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>. <ety>[From its reddish color. See
1st <er>Burrel</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>The botfly or gadfly
of cattle (<spn>Hypoderma bovis</spn>). See <er>Gadfly</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
